# ║
# ║                   🎯 COMPREHENSIVE CHEAT SHEET 🎯
# ║               Never forget gitignore syntax again!
# ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# | 📁 DIRECTORY PATTERNS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
#  dirname/      👈 RECOMMENDED - ignores directories at any level
#  /dirname/     📍 ignores only root-level directory  
#  dirname       ⚠️  ignores both files AND directories (less explicit)
#  **/dirname/   📝 same as dirname/ but more verbose
#  dirname/*     🗂️  ignores contents but tracks empty dirs (rarely used)
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# | 📄 FILE PATTERNS  
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
#  *.ext         🎯 all files with extension (.log, .tmp, etc.)
#  filename.*    📋 files with any extension (README.*, config.*)
#  exact-name    📌 exact filename or dirname match
#  temp-*        🔤 files starting with 'temp-'
#  *-backup      🔚 files ending with '-backup'
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# | 🎭 WILDCARDS & PATTERNS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
#  *             🌟 matches any characters except /
#  **            🌌 matches any characters including /
#  ?             ❓ matches exactly one character
#  [abc]         📝 matches any one character in brackets
#  [a-z]         📏 matches any character in range
#  [!abc]        ❌ matches any character NOT in brackets
#
#  Examples:
#  **/*.log      📊 all .log files anywhere in project
#  src/**/*.test.* 🧪 all test files under src/
#  temp?         🔢 temp1, temp2, tempA, etc.
#  [Tt]emp*      📁 Temp*, temp*, TEMP*, etc.
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# | 🚫 NEGATION PATTERNS (!)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
#  Use ! to UN-ignore files that would otherwise be ignored
#  Negation patterns must come AFTER the broader ignore pattern
#
#  Common Examples:
#
#  # Ignore all of build/ except version info
#  build/
#  !build/version.txt
#  !build/manifest.json
#
#  # Ignore all .env files except the template
#  .env*
#  !.env.example
#
#  # Ignore all logs except error logs
#  *.log
#  !error.log
#  !*-error.log
#
#  # Ignore dist/ but keep important assets
#  dist/
#  !dist/assets/
#  !dist/index.html
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# | 🔧 ADVANCED PATTERNS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
#  /root-only    📍 only matches at repository root
#  path/to/file  🎯 specific path from repo root
#  **/deep/**    🏊 matches at any depth
#  *.{jpg,png}   🖼️  matches multiple extensions (bash-style)
#
#  ⚡ Pro Tips:
#  • Patterns are case-sensitive (except on Windows)
#  • Trailing spaces are ignored
#  • Lines starting with # are comments
#  • Empty lines are ignored
#  • Order matters for negation (!) patterns

